# Frontend Style Guide вҖ” Sem Parar (Zustand-only + Hook Component Pattern)

Welcome to the **Sem Parar Frontend Style Guide**.  
This version consolidates: **Zustand as the only state manager**, **Hook Component pattern** for Screens and Atomic components, **services architecture (SOLID)**, and an **cache pattern**.

> Sit down, have a cup of coffee and read this calmly. вҳ•

---

## :pushpin: Table of Contents

- [Introduction](#introduction)
- [Components & Screens вҖ” Hook Component Pattern](#components--screens--hook-component-pattern)
- [Atomic Components вҖ” Hook Component Pattern](#atomic-components--hook-component-pattern)
